lt' weitgehend unberücksichtigt geblieben. Die hier gesammelten Beiträge fragen daher für diesen Raum nach Aspekten von Identität und Ethnizität unter den Rahmenbedingungen des Hellenismus.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh  aAlexander der Große, Alexandreia, Athen, Hellenismus.1 aDaubner, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEngels, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEngster, Dorit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFreitag, Klaus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFreitag, Klaus, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFündling, Jörg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGünther, Linda-Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichels, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichels, Christoph, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTausend, Klaus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTausend, Sabine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2014z9783110370225oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783412216733423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783412216733.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2014  aZDB-23-DGGb2014